# Skill: Generation Visuelle

Genere des images et videos via les APIs de generation disponibles.

## Images — Seedream 4.5 (prioritaire)

### Via LiteLLM (OpenRouter)
```
POST http://litellm:4000/v1/images/generations
Headers:
  Content-Type: application/json
  Authorization: Bearer ${LITELLM_API_KEY}
Body:
  {
    "model": "seedream",
    "prompt": "<description detaillee de l'image>",
    "n": 1,
    "size": "1024x1024"
  }
```

Cout : ~$0.04/image

### Fallback : DALL-E 3 (via OpenAI)
Meme format, modele "gpt-4o" avec mode image generation.

